data.description: A must see this home, nestled on 4 acres of amazing landscape,  has several beautiful upgrades, including kitchen cabinets, with granite countertops, new bamboo hardwood flooring and carpet less than 3 years old. Updated light fixtures and a primary bathroom ensuite, complete with tiled shower, soaker tub and double vanity, with quartz countertops. In addition to the 3 bedrooms on the main floor, there is a seperate home office with a dedicated entry, breakfast nook, formal dining room and mudroom. Upstairs offers a huge bonus room, with wet bar, two additional bedrooms and a full bath. An oversized 2 car garage is connected with a covered breezeway. Pre-approved buyers only. Recent additions include a 30 x 56 exterior building offering a 2-car garage or workshop and a 3 bay tractor shed. All this and more on 4 beautiful acres bordered on one side by a creek. Too much to list call for your personal tour today!
